replies.body:
this is why i think they need to buff ADC runes and maybe even conqueror to get rid of the power creep and the overwhelming tanks/sustain champs that are starting to take over top again, like {{champion:78}} {{champion:54}} {{champion:86}} {{champion:14}} {{champion:223}} 

Also magic resist needs to be more available. there are barely any MR runes in the game and poke AP champs are completely ruining bot lane because of it {{champion:143}} {{champion:37}} {{champion:99}} {{champion:74}} {{champion:9}} {{champion:63}} support isnt even a support role anymore, its just who can spam out the most spells to poke the other laner out first and ruin the minion wave/ kill them and shove it under causing an auto losing the lane for the opposite team.

I remember when mid {{champion:236}} was very strong, purely just from the PTA damage when it was first released, but they nerfed that shit into the ground along with fleet. {{champion:157}} winrate has plummeted to a negative, {{champion:112}} is taking over top lane. bruisers and tanks cant handle his poke because of the lack of MR runes in the game, the list goes on and on.
